# Project Summary: E-commerce Sales Analysis
## Project Overview
This project analyzes E-commerce sales data using Python to uncover insights into customer behavior, product performance, and overall business trends.

## Tech Stack & Libraries Used
Python: Data processing & analysis
Pandas: Data cleaning & manipulation
NumPy: Numerical operations
Matplotlib & Seaborn: Data visualization
Datetime: Date conversions & time-based analysis
Key Features

✅ Data Preprocessing:
Cleaned raw data by handling missing values & formatting dates.

✅ Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA):
Analyzed sales trends over time.
Identified top-selling products & customer segments.
Evaluated the impact of discounts on revenue.

✅ Visualizations & Insights:
Revenue & profit trends using line charts.
Category-wise performance analysis with bar charts.
Customer segmentation insights with heatmaps.








